The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for enhancing and reconstructing latent fingerprints. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, specifically generative convolutional networks, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper involves biometric comparison, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
